{"tid":1257680,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 中四人生道路問題","createTime":"2019-06-25T16:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T01:01:32.000Z","uid":160075,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2109de35bf64418b419d29b85cf6d3d1e5025287","tid":1257680,"uid":160075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"各位CHING, 我跪求大家比下意見我表弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事緣係我表弟今年中四 ，佢曾經留過一年班，而佢班主任今日話佢好大機會留多年  如果佢不幸留班咁佢就唔想再讀。<br />\n佢同我講日校課程好悶，又唔知讀黎為乜，佢本身就冇諗過考大學。<br />\n <br />\n重點&mdash;＞然後佢班主任就推薦佢去讀職專文憑<br />\n我唔太清楚職專文憑，所以想上網查左下　我見佢網上幅圖顯示中四畢業生讀職專要讀兩年　讀完就可以申請高級文憑？　<br />\n我個人暫時比佢建議係　盡量完成日校課程　因為依加最基本學歷真係中六畢業　<br />\n如果佢今年真係原校留多年　不如轉讀私校　比如遵理日校　聽聞好hea 　最尾都可以有中六畢業證書 然後叫佢去讀 FD　&mdash;&gt;　HD　唔知咁多位巴打有冇咩其他建議比佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde2217e86487aab345c07088b58d8b3fd1a7c45","tid":1257680,"uid":42374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"Vtc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c662929214e6adc59f875bbfd6c4d01a0da4430c","tid":1257680,"uid":243385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"我今年都21 都要去讀職專3年之後上HD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0699fbb748bacc1beb9b6db996243ccec2ed87","tid":1257680,"uid":160075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c662929214e6adc59f875bbfd6c4d01a0da4430c","tid":1257680,"uid":243385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"我今年都21 都要去讀職專3年之後上HD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"你21歲唔係可以用年長生入FD/HD咩?<br />\nCHING 即係我冇理解錯 讀完職專3年就可以上相關HD?"},{"pid":"5b545b735cab3c9d9c4867e0c8f3681b59b835b4","tid":1257680,"uid":142575,"like":20,"dislike"